{"tid":2440981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極恐怖！「塞豆窿」的由來， 知道之後你仲會唔會把細路仔叫做「塞豆窿」？","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T10:52:35.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b10dba7a4473d2aa2f0ce7c8a2e2a8a15a6d9b9","tid":2440981,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"塞豆窿是一種非常殘忍的儀式，傳說古時在洪水為患的地方，防洪的堤壩經常氾濫，便會把一些小孩放進堤壩內的排水口（豆窿）內，他們相信以這個方法便能退洪。現今粵語「塞豆窿」一詞借指小朋友，正是出於此典故。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">亦即係如果你叫細路仔做塞豆窿<br />\n<br />\n其實即係形容緊會將佢塞住喺堤壩排水口<br />\n用來祭天</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac60e7d72eb215c8e15365f427f63ef63aeea4f1","tid":2440981,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"打生樁阿  聽過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0823367485e8dc783b8f29aea81eacc0950f70b3","tid":2440981,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac60e7d72eb215c8e15365f427f63ef63aeea4f1","tid":2440981,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"打生樁阿  聽過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"何文田好似就有打生樁"}]}